'''迈耶斯合成'''（{{lang-en|Meyers synthesis}}），得名於美国化学家艾伯特·I·迈耶斯，指通过[[噁嗪|噁嗪]]水解制取不对称[[醛|醛]]类。<ref>''Aldehydes from dihydro-1,3-oxazines. I. Synthesis of aliphatic aldehydes and their C-1 deuterated derivatives''  [[Albert_I._Meyers|Albert I. Meyers]], Aiko Nabeya, H. Wayne Adickes, Ieva R. Politzer [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] '''1969'''; 91(3); 763-764. {{DOI|10.1021/ja01031a053}}</ref><ref>''Aldehydes from dihydro-1,3-oxazines. II. Synthesis of .alpha.,.beta.-unsaturated aldehydes and their C-1 deuterated derivatives'' Albert I. Meyers, Aiko Nabeya, H. Wayne Adickes, J. Michael Fitzpatrick, G. Ray Malone, and Ieva R. Politzer pp 764 - 765; [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] '''1969''' {{DOI:10.1021/ja01031a054}}</ref><ref>''Aldehydes from dihydro-1,3-oxazines. III. Synthesis of cycloalkanecarboxaldehydes'' Albert I. Meyers, H. Wayne Adickes, Ieva R. Politzer, and Warren N. Beverung pp 765 - 767; [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] '''1969''' {{DOI|10.1021/ja01031a055}}</ref><ref>[[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]], Coll. Vol. 6, p.905 (1988); Vol. 51, p.24 (1971). http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV6P0905.pdf {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV6P0905.pdf |date=20120208144439 }}</ref>

